night games is a 1966 swedish movie directed by mai zetterling and starring ingrid thulin . the film premiered at the 27th venice international film festival where it was considered so controversial that it was shown to the jury in private . the film was also the cause of former child-star shirley temple 's resignation from the san francisco international film festival . temple denounced the film as “ pornography for profit ” and was against it being shown at the festival .